        <abstract> 
<p>Delighted by WBC’s letter about <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. There is now "a great physiologist on our side". "You have done me an essential kindness in checking the odium theologicum in the E[dinburgh] R[eview] … immaterial whether we go quite the same lengths … the principle is everything."</p> 
        </abstract>
